@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam nodesep 120
skinparam ranksep 60
skinparam padding 15
skinparam defaultFontSize 13

actor "User" as AUser

rectangle "Traffic Camera Browser" {
  boundary "Map & Camera Viewer UI" as UI
  control "Live Stream Controller" as LSC
  entity "Camera" as CameraEntity
  entity "HistoryEntry" as HistoryEntity
  entity "User" as UserEntity
}

AUser --> UI : click camera on map
UI --> LSC : request live stream
LSC --> CameraEntity : fetch camera streamUrl
LSC --> UI : deliver live video
LSC --> UserEntity : identify user
LSC --> HistoryEntity : record view\n(LIVE)

note bottom of UI
The platform displays a map showing
the location of each camera. Users
watch videos by clicking a camera.
end note
@enduml